						    <a  href="documents/s173366/Appendix 1 - The Calculation of the Council Tax Base 26-27.pdf"  target="mgDocument173366" title="Link to document &#39;Appendix 1 - The Calculation of the Council Tax Base 26-27&#39; pdf file">Appendix 1 - The Calculation of the Council Tax Base 26-27 <span  class="mgHide" >, item 11.</span>
						    <span  class="mgFileSize" ><img height="12" src="mgimages/logo-pdf-1.gif" width="12" alt="pdf icon" /> PDF 122 KB</span> </a>  </li>

